<para>This INFORMIXDIR environmental variable is set in the [Environment INFORMIXX] section of your OpenLink Session Rules Book.
 This variable is set to the root directory of your server&#39;s Informix installation.
 Moreover, a corresponding INFORMIXDIR variable should exist in the .profile of your Informix user.</para><para>Note: This variable may be set using the Administrative Assistant&#39;s Database Agent Settings Form or Wizard.
